WEBVTT

00:00:08.472 --> 00:00:13.792
Today, we are all here assembled

00:00:13.872 --> 00:00:18.712
in Turkey, in Istanbul,

00:00:18.792 --> 00:00:23.552
to celebrate the resurrection of Christ

00:00:24.232 --> 00:00:30.192
and, with that also, your celebration of your resurrection.

00:00:30.872 --> 00:00:35.312
Christ’s resurrection was a great message for us.

00:00:37.632 --> 00:00:42.032
He won over the death

00:00:42.112 --> 00:00:50.312
and came out of that dead body

00:00:50.952 --> 00:00:55.712
with another body which was living body.

00:00:56.792 --> 00:01:01.451
The body was the same, but one was a dead body

00:01:01.531 --> 00:01:06.136
and another one was a body which was living.

00:01:09.160 --> 00:01:13.952
It’s not only symbolic, it actually happened within.

00:01:14.032 --> 00:01:21.432
After all, He was a divine child, He was a divine person.

00:01:21.512 --> 00:01:26.632
Actually it has happened within. It’s not just a symbolic thing

00:01:26.712 --> 00:01:34.152
that He died and He was resurrected into another person

00:01:34.232 --> 00:01:38.552
or, you can say, into a living person.

00:01:43.872 --> 00:01:50.312
For Him, what is the death? For eternal beings, there are no deaths.

00:01:50.872 --> 00:01:56.312
There’s no death for a person who’s eternal.

00:01:56.392 --> 00:02:00.552
He may, for the time being, look as if He is dead,

00:02:00.632 --> 00:02:03.312
but He can never die.

00:02:03.392 --> 00:02:08.432
Christ was like that, a very, very special incarnation,

00:02:08.512 --> 00:02:14.312
which came on this earth to be reborn out of the dead.

00:02:16.112 --> 00:02:20.712
Now we are also, when we are not yet realized souls,

00:02:20.792 --> 00:02:25.032
when we are not yet enlightened.

00:02:25.112 --> 00:02:31.792
We are also dead in the sense, our awareness is very, very…

00:02:33.552 --> 00:02:38.552
I should say, absolutely dull and dead.

00:02:38.632 --> 00:02:44.552
We can see flowers, we can see faces, we can see buildings,

00:02:44.632 --> 00:02:48.632
we can see cities, we can see all those things.

00:02:48.712 --> 00:02:52.832
All these things we see and we feel we are quite aware,

00:02:52.912 --> 00:02:55.512
which we are not.

00:02:56.032 --> 00:02:58.472
Actual awareness comes to us

00:02:58.552 --> 00:03:01.832
when we cross the limits of our mind,

00:03:01.912 --> 00:03:06.472
go beyond the mind, and this was only possible

00:03:06.552 --> 00:03:11.112
because of the resurrection of Christ.

00:03:11.192 --> 00:03:15.712
He resurrected Himself because He was a divine person.

00:03:15.792 --> 00:03:24.192
But also we are resurrected because we are blessed by Divinity.

00:03:24.272 --> 00:03:29.512
Now this mind of ours, which is in between,

00:03:29.592 --> 00:03:36.192
is controlled by Shri Jesus Christ.

00:03:36.272 --> 00:03:40.232
He controls through your Agnya, both the sides.

00:03:40.312 --> 00:03:45.032
He controls your conditionings and He controls your ego

00:03:45.112 --> 00:03:48.752
and brings a balance in you.

00:03:49.992 --> 00:03:56.712
But when this Agnya Chakra starts sprinkling,

00:03:56.792 --> 00:04:01.592
all sorts of ideas, sometimes reacting,

00:04:01.672 --> 00:04:04.872
sometimes accepting conditionings…

00:04:04.952 --> 00:04:08.992
it is a slave, it is not a free thing,

00:04:09.072 --> 00:04:15.392
because it is working under the influence of your ego

00:04:15.472 --> 00:04:18.552
or your superego.

00:04:20.312 --> 00:04:25.712
For that is the death of our awareness,

00:04:25.792 --> 00:04:32.392
that we cannot, we cannot understand something beyond.

00:04:32.472 --> 00:04:37.992
That there exists a life beyond this, we cannot accept.

00:04:38.072 --> 00:04:40.472
This is… We have seen now

00:04:40.552 --> 00:04:48.312
that we were all in a condition that one was deadened.

00:04:48.392 --> 00:04:51.952
We were feeling bad, we were feeling anxious,

00:04:52.032 --> 00:04:54.832
we were fighting and we were thinking:

00:04:54.912 --> 00:04:59.232
“There’s something wrong with our present life.”

00:04:59.312 --> 00:05:04.952
There’s something definitely which makes us slave,

00:05:05.032 --> 00:05:07.712
by which we are slavish.

00:05:07.792 --> 00:05:13.952
That we realized, no doubt, and we started seeking the Truth.

00:05:14.032 --> 00:05:18.432
We started seeking the Truth in so many ways,

00:05:18.512 --> 00:05:23.192
I know so many were… also went astray,

00:05:23.272 --> 00:05:30.912
and they lost their balance and have fallen into a complete demise.

00:05:30.992 --> 00:05:34.792
But so many of you have been salvaged,

00:05:34.872 --> 00:05:42.112
have been saved by the great example of Christ’s resurrection.

00:05:42.192 --> 00:05:44.792
He had to venture it,

00:05:44.872 --> 00:05:48.672
He had to do it and He worked it out.

00:05:48.752 --> 00:05:53.912
Without Him, our Agnya would not have been that flexible.

00:05:53.992 --> 00:05:56.472
As it is, the human beings

00:05:56.552 --> 00:06:00.512
in the olden times were conditioned very much.

00:06:00.592 --> 00:06:04.912
And when they have become modern, they are full of ego,

00:06:04.992 --> 00:06:06.752
nothing in between.

00:06:06.832 --> 00:06:10.552
With these two influences, we are imprisoned,

00:06:10.632 --> 00:06:15.752
we are absolutely dead people.

00:06:15.832 --> 00:06:19.072
We have no sensitivity for anything.

00:06:19.152 --> 00:06:22.912
I’ve seen now… even today, you can see

00:06:22.992 --> 00:06:25.432
about things are happening across,

00:06:25.512 --> 00:06:30.672
is people are very anxious to kill each other.

00:06:30.752 --> 00:06:34.272
Human beings want to kill human beings, can you imagine?

00:06:34.352 --> 00:06:40.672
Such a stupid thing that we should kill our kith and kin.

00:06:40.752 --> 00:06:44.112
Then, there are children who are killing,

00:06:44.192 --> 00:06:49.552
parents that are killing, no relationship is accepted.

00:06:49.632 --> 00:06:55.472
It’s a sign of a person whose awareness is completely dead.

00:06:55.552 --> 00:06:57.512
In our awareness, at least

00:06:57.592 --> 00:07:01.992
we should have feelings of compassion and love.

00:07:02.072 --> 00:07:07.472
But that one is lost, it’s not there, we don’t have it.

00:07:07.552 --> 00:07:11.592
The whole world is a flame, when you read about

00:07:11.672 --> 00:07:13.792
all the wars that are going on,

00:07:13.872 --> 00:07:15.872
the way they are killing children,

00:07:15.952 --> 00:07:21.192
the way they are destroying human beings.

00:07:22.872 --> 00:07:27.232
It is a wrong attitude

00:07:27.312 --> 00:07:31.712
that with destruction of human beings, things will improve.

00:07:31.792 --> 00:07:34.512
It’s a very, very wrong concept

00:07:34.592 --> 00:07:39.712
that by destroying them, one can achieve something.

00:07:41.872 --> 00:07:46.392
Our work in Sahaja Yoga is doing well, I must say,

00:07:46.472 --> 00:07:51.592
but it has to stop this horrible attitude of human beings

00:07:51.672 --> 00:07:53.752
to destroy.

00:07:53.832 --> 00:07:56.472
So you might ask then: “What to do, Mother?

00:07:56.552 --> 00:08:01.032
What to do to stop this destruction?”

00:08:01.112 --> 00:08:03.512
Answer is in the life of Christ.

00:08:03.592 --> 00:08:05.592
You resurrect people,

00:08:05.672 --> 00:08:10.032
you resurrect them, enlighten them, bring them

00:08:10.112 --> 00:08:15.032
to a state where they understand what is right and what is wrong.

00:08:15.112 --> 00:08:19.552
Let them feel, let them feel the compassion

00:08:19.632 --> 00:08:21.713
and love that is within you.

00:08:21.793 --> 00:08:30.233
So, how can we now join together to make a full effort,

00:08:31.033 --> 00:08:35.193
a full effort, to tell people that:

00:08:35.273 --> 00:08:40.953
“What are you doing? Why are you doing it?

00:08:41.033 --> 00:08:43.753
What is the need to do such things?”

00:08:43.833 --> 00:08:48.353
On one side is, we can say, a mass destruction

00:08:48.433 --> 00:08:54.913
through stupidity, another side is your own self-destruction.

00:08:56.473 --> 00:09:03.193
Take to drinking, take to other self-destructive things

00:09:03.273 --> 00:09:06.113
which are immoral,

00:09:06.193 --> 00:09:10.353
that’s very easily available, and people like it very much.

00:09:10.433 --> 00:09:15.753
They don’t like when you talk that: “This is destructive.”

00:09:15.833 --> 00:09:20.593
So, either we destroy others or destroy ourselves.

00:09:20.673 --> 00:09:27.033
Christ was destroyed by others and He resurrected by Himself.

00:09:27.113 --> 00:09:29.873
So we are also in the same position now.

00:09:29.953 --> 00:09:33.113
I know many a times Sahaja Yoga was challenged.

00:09:33.193 --> 00:09:36.086
Now it’s much better, not so bad…

00:09:36.166 --> 00:09:39.033
was challenged and there were so many problems.

00:09:39.113 --> 00:09:43.073
But now it’s smoothing down,

00:09:43.153 --> 00:09:46.553
because that’s the Truth, that’s the Reality,

00:09:46.633 --> 00:09:48.713
that’s what is Divinity.

00:09:48.793 --> 00:09:51.353
So, you should not be afraid.

00:09:51.433 --> 00:09:58.033
All these funny ideas about Sahaja Yoga also will die out.

00:09:58.113 --> 00:10:02.713
It’s a resurrection, not only of you people,

00:10:02.793 --> 00:10:07.433
but also of your ideologies.

00:10:07.513 --> 00:10:09.713
Now the ideologies change,

00:10:09.793 --> 00:10:13.993
that our awareness should be enlightened.

00:10:14.073 --> 00:10:16.793
We should have light in our awareness.

00:10:16.873 --> 00:10:20.113
This has come suddenly through Sahaja Yoga to people, that:

00:10:20.193 --> 00:10:22.233
“If you don’t have the light,

00:10:22.313 --> 00:10:27.753
how can you go further in the right path?”

00:10:27.833 --> 00:10:33.033
It’s not easy to describe Christ’s life, how He went through that.

00:10:33.113 --> 00:10:38.473
He died so young and brutally He was killed.

00:10:38.553 --> 00:10:43.313
But still all that, He resurrected Himself.

00:10:43.393 --> 00:10:47.553
He came out of all that, came out of that ordeal.

00:10:47.633 --> 00:10:51.353
So for us also, when we are in Sahaja Yoga problems,

00:10:51.433 --> 00:10:54.899
we should know we have a power to resurrect ourselves.

00:10:54.979 --> 00:10:58.673
No one can destroy us! No one can finish us off,

00:10:58.753 --> 00:11:03.073
because we have a power to resurrect ourselves.

00:11:03.153 --> 00:11:06.233
This special power that we have to resurrect,

00:11:06.313 --> 00:11:11.327
you should all the time understand and feel it and meditate on that.

00:11:11.927 --> 00:11:16.007
You are quite aware, you are born in modern times,

00:11:16.087 --> 00:11:18.887
and at this time, when we think of Christ,

00:11:18.967 --> 00:11:21.966
we should know what a life it was,

00:11:22.046 --> 00:11:24.967
what a grand personality it was,

00:11:25.047 --> 00:11:28.687
that He subjected to this kind of a torture.

00:11:28.767 --> 00:11:31.800
He could have destroyed all of them in no time.

00:11:31.880 --> 00:11:35.447
He was so powerful, such a powerful personality,

00:11:35.527 --> 00:11:39.847
but He did not! He forgave them.

00:11:39.927 --> 00:11:42.687
He gave you the message of forgiveness,

00:11:42.767 --> 00:11:45.607
the greatest force that can work out.

00:11:45.687 --> 00:11:48.580
Now also, you should surrender yourself

00:11:48.660 --> 00:11:53.447
to this idea of forgiveness and really try to forgive.

00:11:53.527 --> 00:11:57.287
You’ll be amazed, you will feel very much peaceful, very happy,

00:11:57.367 --> 00:12:02.287
and the person who has tortured you will come round.

00:12:02.967 --> 00:12:07.607
What we have to do is now to transform people. That’s our job.

00:12:07.687 --> 00:12:10.367
We have to transform them. We are transformed.

00:12:10.447 --> 00:12:13.807
We are at a point, we can call it, we are resurrected.

00:12:13.887 --> 00:12:16.887
We have to resurrect the whole world, that’s our job,

00:12:16.967 --> 00:12:20.367
so that all these fights, all these quarrels,

00:12:20.447 --> 00:12:24.887
all these falsehoods will just be finished.

00:12:24.967 --> 00:12:28.767
For us, Christ is our leader, who has done this for us.

00:12:28.847 --> 00:12:30.687
He came as an ordinary human being,

00:12:30.767 --> 00:12:32.767
lived like an ordinary human being,

00:12:32.847 --> 00:12:35.327
with all these powers within Him.

00:12:35.407 --> 00:12:37.767
He never used them to destroy.

00:12:37.847 --> 00:12:42.687
In the same way, we can also with love and affection,

00:12:42.767 --> 00:12:47.647
we can also really come out of our deaths,

00:12:47.727 --> 00:12:50.047
come out of our misgivings,

00:12:50.127 --> 00:12:53.527
come out of our destructive nature.

00:12:53.607 --> 00:13:00.047
This destructive nature is the most dangerous thing for Yogis.

00:13:00.127 --> 00:13:06.767
That’s the only hope we have, that Sahaja Yogis are resurrected.

00:13:06.847 --> 00:13:11.247
Only thing I know is that,

00:13:11.327 --> 00:13:16.207
if we have so many Sahaja Yogis, this world will change.

00:13:16.287 --> 00:13:18.047
This world has to change.

00:13:18.127 --> 00:13:20.527
But your progress should go on,

00:13:20.607 --> 00:13:25.327
you should progress more and more, not you should not regress back.

00:13:25.407 --> 00:13:28.207
For small things here and there, don’t worry!

00:13:28.287 --> 00:13:31.127
You have a very great responsibility,

00:13:31.207 --> 00:13:36.607
and that responsibility is to transform the human beings.

00:13:36.687 --> 00:13:41.687
That’s your due. How many have you transformed?

00:13:41.767 --> 00:13:47.047
How many have you changed? It’s all right for men or women.

00:13:47.127 --> 00:13:50.367
You have to change people, this is your job

00:13:50.447 --> 00:13:54.047
and this is the power you have got from Christ,

00:13:54.127 --> 00:13:57.367
that you have to change them, transform them

00:13:57.447 --> 00:14:00.967
into the new world of happiness and joy

00:14:01.047 --> 00:14:07.367
which we call it as the Sahaj Nirmal Dharma.

00:14:07.447 --> 00:14:11.207
If it works out, if it really works out,

00:14:11.287 --> 00:14:16.087
think of the world, how beautiful it will become for us!

00:14:16.167 --> 00:14:18.887
It’s the duty of every Sahaja Yogi

00:14:18.967 --> 00:14:24.127
to go into this kind of a new venture

00:14:24.207 --> 00:14:29.367
and try to find out how many people he can convert

00:14:29.447 --> 00:14:32.447
and how many people he can bring round.

00:14:32.527 --> 00:14:36.367
I hope next time we’ll have doubled the number of people

00:14:36.447 --> 00:14:40.687
that are here from all these eight countries who are hosting now.

00:14:40.767 --> 00:14:43.167
All My love to you all.

00:14:43.247 --> 00:14:47.807
Great days are waiting us.

00:14:47.887 --> 00:14:53.687
We have to now understand only our responsibility.

00:14:53.767 --> 00:14:57.367
Main thing is how many people we have converted,

00:14:57.447 --> 00:15:00.293
how many people we have resurrected.

00:15:00.373 --> 00:15:02.687
That is the record, not what,

00:15:02.767 --> 00:15:06.527
how many Pujas you have attended and all that.
It’s not so important.

00:15:06.607 --> 00:15:10.167
Pujas are just to give you strength and to give you power,

00:15:10.247 --> 00:15:14.367
but they are not your work. That’s not your work.

00:15:14.447 --> 00:15:16.887
For your work, you can take from Pujas

00:15:16.967 --> 00:15:19.167
all the strength that you need.

00:15:19.247 --> 00:15:24.607
But if you don’t use this power, then what’s the use?

00:15:24.687 --> 00:15:27.407
So now, I leave it to you to remember

00:15:27.487 --> 00:15:31.327
that you are resurrected and you have to resurrect others.

00:15:31.407 --> 00:15:33.767
It’s a very, very important job

00:15:33.847 --> 00:15:37.661
at this time of complete turmoil and destruction.

00:15:37.741 --> 00:15:40.187
May God bless you!